  "text": "This mechanism utilises active contents such as a JavaScript or ActiveX [CITATION_1] to make the users knowingly (by authorizing to run the active content) or unknowingly download attackers malicious contents while browsing a compromised or specially crafted web page [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] . Adversaries may include the malicious code in a seamless object like an advert or a widget and eventually lure a victim to download a Trojan without intending to do so [CITATION_4] .",
